10) UI wiring notes
- Planner: select crops/beds → buildGardenPlan → setPlan & setTasks.
- Tasks: checklist emits garden.tasks.updated; power-hour like Cleaning module.
- Water/Soil: buildIrrigationPlan → timers; “Apply” emits garden.irrigation.applied.
- Harvest: onConfirm → computeHarvestDelta → show delta modal; Confirm → inventory & savings.
- Inventory/Savings: show produce[], monthly savings; “Move to root cellar” sets location/date.
- Preservation: open modal (can/freeze/dehydrate/ferment) + LabelPrinter (reuse from Cooking).
- Collaboration: goal → optimizeAllocations → schedule → conflicts → finalize → calendar.synced.

11) Organic mix recipes (WaterSoilPanel cards)
- Compost Tea (aerated): 5gal water + 2c finished compost in mesh + 1 tbsp molasses; aerate 24h; soil drench AM.
- Fish Emulsion: 1–2 tbsp/gal (per label); no foliar at high heat.
- Calcium Boost (eggshell vinegar): 1c baked shells + 2c vinegar; steep 2–4 wks; 1–2 tbsp/gal drench.
- Potassium Boost: 5 banana peels in 1 gal water, 48h; dilute 1:5; apply at flowering.
- Neem Foliar: 1 tsp neem + 1/2 tsp unscented soap / quart; dusk/dawn; avoid blooms.

